## radius is a half of diameter
## are of circle is pie*radius**2
## area of rectrangle is length*width
diameter = input("what is the diameter")
radius = int(diameter)/2
circle= 3.1415*int(radius**2)
print(circle)
length = input("what is the width")
width = input("what is the length")
square= int(length)*int(width)
print(square)

